      "role": "user",
      "content": "friends and family wont help, they'll just judge me or feel sorry for me. and a counselor doesnt stop the collections calls. it's not just stress, it's like the math doesn't work. no matter what i do, the hole just gets deeper. it feels like a trap that's already closed. how can anyone actually \"navigate\" through something that is mathematically impossible to fix?",
